r assertion**: Throws if any console errors detected after test completes\n\n**Wrapped goto signature:**\n```typescript\npage.goto = async (url: string, options?: Parameters<typeof page.goto>[1]) => {\n  // ... inject CSS + pause SVG animations + wait fonts + 300ms\n  return response;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 8. **Playwright Configuration**\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.config.ts`\n\n**Key settings:**\n- **Test dir**: `e2e/`\n- **Project filter**: Only runs tests matching `visual/**/*.spec.ts`\n- **Viewport**: 1280×1080 (Desktop Chrome)\n- **Snapshot threshold**: `maxDiffPixelRatio: 0.015` (1.5% pixel variance default; can be overridden per test)\n- **Snapshot path template**: `{testDir}/__snapshots__/{testFilePath}/{arg}{ext}`\n- **Web server**: Vite on port 3000 (customizable via `PLAYWRIGHT_PLATFORM_PORT`)\n- **Mock mode**: `VITE_MOCK_MODE=true` (simulated data, no backend required)\n- **Retries**: 0 (fail fast)\n- **Workers**: 1 (sequential, deterministic)\n\n---\n\n### 9. **Routes Defined in App.tsx**\n\nClose Call route definitions (lines 376, 385):\n```typescript\n<Route path=\"/close-call\" element={<CloseCallPage />} />\n<Route path=\"/close-call/:roundId\" element={<CloseCallRoundPage />} />\n```\n\nThe `/close-call` route is fully integrated. The `/close-call/:roundId` route supports deep-linking to specific rounds (similar to `/coinflip/:matchId` and `/lord-of-rngs/:matchId`).\n\n---\n\n### 10. **Summary Table: Visual Test Coverage by Game**\n\n| Game | routes.spec.ts | states.spec.ts | Total Snapshots |\n|------|---|---|---|\n| Coinflip | ✅ | ✅ (3 variants) | 4 |\n| Lord of RNGs | ✅ | ✅ (4 variants) | 5 |\n| Close Call | ✅ | ❌ | 1 |\n| Crash | ✅ | ❌ | 1 |\n| Game of Trades | ✅ | ❌ | 1 |\n\n**Close Call is the least covered** — only has the basic route snapshot, missing all state variants.\n\n---\n\n### Key Files Referenced\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/routes.spec.t